<Layout title="FYTS" description="DragonForgeNexus' FYTS program Partnerships"  page="/Partners/FYTS">
	<div class="p-6">
		<div class="text-4xl">About the FYTS program:</div>
		<br />
		<div class="text-2xl">What is the FYTS program?</div>
		The the FYTS program is a program for content creators to be able to easily help each other, hang out, meet other creators, and get their uploads/streams announced in discord!
		<br />
		<br />
		<div class="text-2xl">How do I join the FYTS program?</div>
		afew steps:
		<ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
			<li>make sure you meet the requirements <a href="./requirements">here</a></li>
			<li>Join the discord*, to find the join link go <a href="../DragonForgeMedia/Discord">here</a></li>
			<li>Make a ticket in #tickets under "FYTS"</li>
			<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
				<li>For the "channel ID" spot of the form, you need your youtube channel id, If you don't know where to find it go <a href="https://www.youtube.com/account_advanced">here</a></li>
			</ul>
			<li>hit submit and we will review your request</li>
		</ol>
		<div class="text-xl">You are not guaranteed to be excepted!</div>
		<br />
		<div class="text-2xl">I have applied, what should I expect?</div>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
			<li>being held to a higher standard than even MODS.</li>
			<li>You will get the <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);">@YouTuber</span> and/or <span style="color: rgb(145, 70, 255); background-color: rgba(145, 70, 255, 0.1);">@Twitch Streamer</span> role(s) on discord depending on what you signed up for</li>
			<li>You will get your channel(s) added to the welcome message.</li>
			<li>Your new videos and/or streams will get automatically announced in the #fyts-announcements channel on the discord</li>
		</ul>
